{"tid":911893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"華裔傳教士非法登禁閉島 慘遭原住民亂箭射殺！","createTime":"2018-11-22T09:11:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T09:21:20.000Z","uid":75406,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a68d7c8b26220a19cf27b8a3487e9ee8d3921444","tid":911893,"uid":75406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n一名據信是美籍華裔的男子上周五(16日)在印度安達曼群島獨遊探險。他登上一座嚴禁登岸的島嶼後，不幸被政府保護的原住民部落以亂箭射殺。當地警方已將此一事件列為謀殺案，並逮捕7人。<br />\n<br />\n27歲的趙約翰(譯音，John Allen Chau)先是登上當地漁民的漁船，然後再獨自划獨木舟靠近偏遠的北森蒂納爾島(North Sentinel island)。<br />\n<br />\n印 度當局表示，他才登岸沒多久就遭到當地原住民發箭攻擊。他中箭後試圖逃跑，但慘遭原住民用繩子綁住他的脖子拖行。<br />\n<br />\n目擊此一事件的數名漁民嚇壞了，連忙逃離現場。第二天他們返回案發地點，在岸邊發現趙約翰 的屍體。當局周三(21日)證實，死者是中箭身亡，同時逮捕7名涉及協助趙約翰非法登岸的漁民。媒體指出，趙約翰是一名傳教士。<br />\n<br />\n北森蒂納爾島位處印度以東的孟加拉灣，島嶼周圍禁絕航行，連印度海軍也不例外。該島上僅有150名原住民，他們向來對入侵者抱著敵意。<br />\n<br />\n為了保護當地原住民的部落文化以及避免他們感染疾病，法律規定外來者不得跟他們接觸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com.tw/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1312242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.tw%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253Fnews_id%253D1312242&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=a4957642\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.tw/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1312242</a>"},{"pid":"447e4b70741e547b090b4db509df1c2d1b8c3a29","tid":911893,"uid":75406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:13:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1312242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253Fnews_id%253D1312242&d=qAGctaA1C1X%2F6UEGp%2F687Gi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9667a38a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3Fnews_id%3D1312242</a>"},{"pid":"2f7bfd17e4c37f0a8dc9312f2361622fbaf1c36a","tid":911893,"uid":119223,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:18:45.000Z","msg":"上帝既考驗"},{"pid":"b9b4fad7e43a2d758e31a1f33e271545e82661cf","tid":911893,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"悟空，你又曳曳啦<br />\n<br />\nOnly you....."},{"pid":"2fce6e8561295e4a9729a864857d17e289d6dad2","tid":911893,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-22T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"耶撚真係以為自己大晒可以打橫行咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}